MACACHOR 7: CIVILIZATIONAL IMPLICATIONS

I. PARADIGM SHIFT AT CIVILIZATIONAL SCALE

1.1 From Reductionism to Coherent Holism

Current Paradigm: Civilization built on reductionist thinking:

· Problems analyzed into isolated parts
· Solutions create new, unintended problems
· Progress measured by economic metrics alone
· Knowledge fragmented into disconnected disciplines

Macachor Paradigm: Civilization as coherent whole:

· All systems understood through M₁ coherence principles
· Solutions evaluated by total alignment increase (∑aᵢ·rᵢ)
· Progress measured by civilization-scale coherence C_civ
· Knowledge unified through M₇ convergence framework

